# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and the working tree.
# The index is already 100% LF; this stops checkout-time CRLF conversion on
# Windows (and the warning spam that comes with it) for every contributor.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lockfiles and generated artifacts keep LF too (covered by the rule above);
# binaries are listed explicitly so autodetection never mangles them.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.woff2 binary
